===Etymology 2===
From {{inh|en|enm|pounde}}, {{m|enm|ponde}}, {{m|enm|pund}}, from {{inh|en|ang|pund|t=an enclosure}}, related to {{cog|ang|pyndan|t=to enclose, shut up, dam, impound}}. Compare also {{cog|ang|pynd|t=a [[cistern]], lake}}.

