#* {{quote-song|en|author=Bob Dylan|authorlink=Bob Dylan|year=1964|title=Motorpsycho Nitemare|passage=I '''pounded''' on a farmhouse / Lookin' for a place to stay / I was mighty, mighty tired / I had come a long, long way}}
