<references/>

In order to allow [[Module:syllables]] to count syllables, the disyllabic sequence {{IPAchar|/iə/}} must be transcribed with a period to mark the syllable break &ndash; {{IPAchar|/i.ə/}} &ndash; so that it will not be confused with the New Zealand diphthong {{IPAchar|/iə/}}.

{{IPAchar|/ɹ/}} in the vowel plus {{IPAchar|/ɹ/}} sequences is sometimes replaced with {{IPAchar|/ɚ/}}: {{IPAchar|/ðɛɚ/}} instead of {{IPAchar|/ðɛɹ/}}. In order to keep [[Module:syllables]] from counting {{IPAchar|/ɚ/}} as a syllable, add the non-syllabic diacritic: {{IPAchar|/ðɛɚ̯/}}.

