# {{lb|en|now|historical}} A type of [[ale]] traditionally brewed in October. {{defdate|from 18th c.}}
#*'''1751''', {{w|Tobias Smollett}}, ''The Adventures of Peregrine Pickle'', vol. IV, ch. 114:
#*:[T]he gate of a large <i>chateau</i>, of a most noble and venerable appearance […] induced them to alight and view the apartments, contrary to their first intention of drinking a glass of his '''October''' at the door.

