* {{a|GA}} {{IPA|en|/ˈwɛnzdeɪ/|/ˈwɛnzdi/}}
* {{a|NZ}} {{IPA|en|/ˈwenzdæe/}}
* {{a|Scotland}} {{IPA|en|/ˈwɛ(ʔə)nzde/}}
