==Middle English==

===Alternative forms===
* {{alter|enm|Wednesdei|Wodnesdai|Wedonesday}}

===Etymology===
From {{inh|enm|ang|*wēdnesdæġ}}, a by-form of {{m|ang|wōdnesdæġ}}, from {{inh|enm|gmw-pro|*Wōdanas dag}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|enm|/ˈwɛ(d)n(i)zdɛi̯/}}

===Proper noun===
{{enm-proper noun}}

# {{l|en|Wednesday}}

