===Etymology 2===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|la|minūtus||small", "petty}}, perfect passive participle of {{m|la|minuō||make smaller}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{a|UK}} {{enPR|mīnyo͞ot'}}, {{IPA|en|/maɪˈnjuːt/}}
* {{a|US}} {{enPR|mīn(y)o͞ot'|mən(y)o͞ot'}}, {{IPA|en|/maɪˈn(j)ut/|/məˈn(j)ut/}}
* {{audio|en|en-us-minute-adjective.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{rhymes|en|uːt}}

