{{en-adj|er}}

# Very [[small]].
#: {{ux|en|They found only '''minute''' quantities of chemical residue on his clothing.}}
#: {{syn|en|infinitesimal|insignificant|minuscule|tiny|trace}}
#: {{ant|en|big|enormous|colossal|huge|significant|tremendous|vast}}
# Very [[careful]] and [[exact]], giving small [[detail]]s.
#* {{quote-journal|en|year=2013|month=July-August|author=[http://www.americanscientist.org/authors/detail/fenella-saunders Fenella Saunders]|magazine={{w|American Scientist}}
