===Noun===
{{en-noun|-|s}}

# An [[exchange]] of goods or services without the use of [[money]].
#: ''We had no money so we had to live by '''barter'''.''
# The goods or services used in such an exchange.
#: ''The man used his watch as '''barter''' to pay for his tab.''

