#: {{syn|en|noun|q1=sensu stricto|noun substantive}}
#: {{hyper|en|noun|q1=sensu lato}}
# Part of a [[text]] that carries the [[meaning]], such as [[word]]s and their [[ordering]].
#: {{cot|en|accidental}}

