* {{a|US}}:
*: {{enPR|no͞o-män'ō-ŭl-trə-mī-krə-skäpʹĭk-sĭl'ē-kō-väl-kā-nō-kō-nē-ōʹsĭs}};
* {{IPA|en|/nuˌmɑːnoʊʌltɹəmaɪkɹoʊˈskɑːpɪkˌsɪlɪkoʊvɑːlkeɪnoʊkoʊniˈoʊsɪs/}};
* {{audio|en|en-us-pneumonoultramicroscopicsilicovolcanoconiosis.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{hyphenation|en|pneu|mon|o|ul|tra|mi|cro|scop|ic|sil|i|co|vol|ca|no|co|ni|o|sis}}
{{rel-bottom}}

