===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|name}}, {{m|enm|nome}}, from {{inh|en|ang|nama}}, {{m|ang|noma}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*namô}}, from {{inh|en|ine-pro|*h₁nómn̥}}. Cognates include {{cog|la|nomen}} ({{cog|es|nombre}}). Possible cognates outside of Indo-European include {{cog|fi|nimi}}.

