===Etymology===
[[File:GreekDigamma-01.png|50px|Greek Ϝ, the source for Latin F]]
Modification of upper case Latin letter {{m|mul|F}}, from Greek {{m|mul|sc=Grek|Ϝ|tr=W||Digamma}}, from [[Phœnician]] {{m|mul|sc=Phnx|𐤅|tr=W||waw}}, the ultimate source being probably Egyptian.

===Letter===
{{mul-letter|upper=F|lower=f|sc=Latn}}

# The sixth letter of the [[Appendix:Latin script|basic modern Latin alphabet]].

