===Etymology 2===

====Symbol====
{{en-symbol}}

# {{lb|en|music}} {{n-g|The name of the fourth tone of the model scale, or scale of C. F sharp (F♯) is a tone intermediate between F and G.}}

=====Derived terms=====
* F clef: the [[bass]] clef. See under [[clef]].

