===Preposition===
{{head|nb|preposition}}
# {{lb|nb|economics}} [[from]]; (i.e. delivered) for the seller's expense at a location and forwarded for the buyer's expense
#: {{ux|nb|'''ab''' Frankfurt|'''from''' Frankfurt|inline=1}}
